<db:section xml:id="angle-prop">
<db:title>angle : real</db:title>
<db:para>This property defines the starting angle where the color at the gradient position of 0.0 is rendered. Colors at larger position values are rendered into larger angle values and blended seamlessly. Angle values increase clockwise.</db:para>
